INSERT INTO Movies (Title, ShortDescription, LongDescription, Rating, Rated, Saved) 
VALUES
('Inception', 'A thriller about dreams within dreams.', 'Dom Cobb is a skilled thief, the absolute best in the dangerous art of extraction: stealing valuable secrets from deep within the subconscious during the dream state. Cobb is offered a chance to have his criminal history erased if he can accomplish the impossible-planting an idea into someone’s mind, known as inception. As Cobb and his team navigate layers of dreams within dreams, they face psychological traps and the haunting memories of Cobb’s past, where the line between reality and illusion begins to blur.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Interstellar', 'A space epic exploring survival.', 'In a future where Earth is dying, former NASA pilot Cooper joins a team of explorers on a mission through a wormhole to find a new habitable planet for humanity. The journey tests the limits of human endurance and emotion, as the crew faces perilous alien worlds, the relentless passage of time, and the heartbreaking separation from loved ones. The film explores the power of love, sacrifice, and the human will to survive, culminating in a mind-bending confrontation with the mysteries of space and time.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Dark Knight', 'Batman faces his greatest enemy.', 'Batman forms an uneasy alliance with police lieutenant Jim Gordon and district attorney Harvey Dent to dismantle Gotham’s organized crime. Their efforts are upended by the Joker, an anarchic criminal mastermind who unleashes chaos and tests Batman’s moral limits. As the Joker’s schemes escalate, Batman faces impossible choices that threaten his identity and the city’s fragile hope.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Forrest Gump', 'A man recounts his extraordinary life.', 'Forrest Gump, a man with a kind heart and limited intellect, recounts his extraordinary life story, crossing paths with key moments in American history. From playing college football to fighting in Vietnam and running across the country, Forrest’s unwavering optimism and love for his childhood friend Jenny guide him through triumphs and heartbreaks. His story is a testament to the power of innocence, perseverance, and destiny.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Matrix', 'A hacker learns reality is a simulation.', 'Computer hacker Neo discovers that reality as he knows it is an elaborate simulation called the Matrix, created by intelligent machines to enslave humanity. Guided by the enigmatic Morpheus and the skilled Trinity, Neo must accept his role as “the One” and lead a rebellion against the machines. As he learns to bend the rules of the Matrix, Neo confronts powerful agents and questions the nature of reality itself.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Shawshank Redemption', 'A story of hope inside a prison.', 'Wrongly convicted of murdering his wife, banker Andy Dufresne is sentenced to life in the harsh Shawshank Prison. Over decades, Andy forms a deep friendship with fellow inmate Red, maintaining hope and dignity in the face of brutality and despair. Through acts of quiet resistance and ingenuity, Andy inspires those around him and ultimately engineers a daring escape, proving that hope can flourish even behind bars.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Gladiator', 'A Roman general seeks revenge.', 'Roman general Maximus is betrayed and forced into slavery after the emperor’s murder by his own son, Commodus. Driven by grief and a thirst for justice, Maximus becomes a gladiator, rising through the ranks with his unmatched skill and courage. His quest for vengeance leads him to the heart of Rome, where he confronts Commodus in a battle that will determine the fate of the empire and his own redemption.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Titanic', 'A tragic love story on a doomed ship.', 'On the ill-fated maiden voyage of the RMS Titanic, aristocratic Rose and penniless artist Jack fall deeply in love despite the constraints of their social classes. Their romance blossoms as the ship sails across the Atlantic, but tragedy strikes when the Titanic hits an iceberg. Amidst the chaos and sinking of the ship, Jack and Rose fight for survival, making heartbreaking sacrifices in a story of love and loss.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Godfather', 'A crime family’s rise and struggles.', 'Chronicling the powerful Corleone crime family, The Godfather follows patriarch Vito Corleone as he navigates the dangerous underworld of organized crime. When an attempt is made on his life, his reluctant son Michael is drawn into the family business, setting off a chain of events that will forever alter the family’s destiny. The film explores themes of loyalty, power, and the corrupting influence of ambition, as Michael transforms from outsider to ruthless leader.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Saving Private Ryan', 'A powerful WWII survival story.', 'During the chaos of World War II’s D-Day invasion, Captain John Miller leads a squad of U.S. soldiers on a perilous mission behind enemy lines to find and bring home Private James Ryan, whose brothers have all been killed in action. As they traverse war-torn France, the men confront the horrors of battle and grapple with the meaning of duty, sacrifice, and humanity. The film is renowned for its realistic depiction of combat and its poignant exploration of the cost of war.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Avatar', 'An adventure on the alien world Pandora.', 'On the lush alien world of Pandora, paraplegic Marine Jake Sully is given a chance to walk again by inhabiting a genetically engineered Na’vi body. As he integrates with the native tribe and learns their ways, Jake becomes torn between following orders to help humans exploit Pandora’s resources and protecting the world he has come to love. The film dazzles with groundbreaking visuals and delivers a powerful message about environmentalism, identity, and the clash of cultures.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Avengers: Endgame', 'The Avengers unite for one last fight.', 'After the devastating events of Infinity War, the surviving Avengers and their allies must regroup and devise a plan to reverse the destruction caused by Thanos. Facing their greatest challenge yet, the heroes embark on a time-traveling quest to recover the Infinity Stones and restore the universe. Endgame delivers epic battles, emotional farewells, and a triumphant conclusion to over a decade of interconnected superhero stories.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Joker', 'A dark origin story of a villain.', 'Arthur Fleck, a struggling comedian in Gotham City, is pushed to the brink by a society that disregards and mistreats him. As his mental health deteriorates, Arthur’s transformation into the infamous Joker ignites a violent uprising and challenges the city’s moral fabric. The film offers a haunting character study of isolation, madness, and the consequences of neglecting society’s most vulnerable.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Toy Story', 'Toys come to life when humans aren’t looking.', 'When Andy’s favorite toy, Woody, feels threatened by the arrival of flashy new space ranger Buzz Lightyear, the two embark on a wild adventure after being separated from their owner. As Woody and Buzz learn to work together, they discover the true meaning of friendship and loyalty. Toy Story blends humor, heart, and groundbreaking animation to create a timeless tale about growing up and letting go.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Lion King', 'A young lion must reclaim his throne.', 'Young lion cub Simba is destined to become king, but his life is upended when his uncle Scar orchestrates the death of Simba’s father, Mufasa. Fleeing into exile, Simba grows up with new friends Timon and Pumbaa, eventually finding the courage to return and reclaim his rightful place. The Lion King is a sweeping coming-of-age story about identity, responsibility, and the enduring bonds of family.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Parasite', 'A dark social satire on class struggle.', 'The impoverished Kim family cunningly infiltrates the lives of the wealthy Park family by securing jobs as tutors and servants. As the Kims weave their web of deception, a shocking discovery sets off a chain reaction of greed, class conflict, and violence. Parasite is a darkly comedic social thriller that exposes the deep divides and hidden connections between rich and poor.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Grand Budapest Hotel', 'A concierge and his adventures.', 'Set in a fictional European country, the film follows the adventures of the meticulous concierge Gustave H. and his loyal protégé, Zero. When Gustave is accused of murder after inheriting a priceless painting, the duo embark on a madcap journey involving eccentric guests, a ruthless family, and a looming war. The Grand Budapest Hotel is a visually delightful and whimsical tale of friendship, loyalty, and the fading elegance of a bygone era.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Pulp Fiction', 'Crime stories interwoven with iconic dialogue.', 'Told in a nonlinear fashion, Pulp Fiction interweaves the lives of hitmen, a boxer, a gangster’s wife, and petty criminals in a series of darkly comedic and violent vignettes. The film’s sharp dialogue, iconic scenes, and unexpected twists create a unique tapestry of crime and redemption. Quentin Tarantino’s masterpiece is a genre-defining exploration of fate, morality, and pop culture.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring', 'The beginning of a legendary fantasy quest.', 'In the mythical land of Middle-earth, young hobbit Frodo Baggins inherits a powerful ring that must be destroyed to prevent the rise of the dark lord Sauron. Joined by a fellowship of heroes, Frodo embarks on a perilous quest through treacherous landscapes and ancient ruins. The film launches an epic trilogy about friendship, courage, and the struggle between good and evil.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Star Wars: Episode V - The Empire Strikes Back', 'The rebels face their darkest hour.', 'After a crushing defeat on the ice planet Hoth, Luke Skywalker seeks Jedi training from Master Yoda while Han Solo, Princess Leia, and their allies evade the relentless pursuit of Darth Vader. As the Rebels face mounting danger, Luke confronts shocking truths about his heritage. The Empire Strikes Back is celebrated for its darker tone, complex characters, and one of cinema’s most iconic plot twists.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Back to the Future', 'A teenager time-travels accidentally.', 'Teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent thirty years into the past in a time-traveling DeLorean invented by the eccentric Doc Brown. Stranded in 1955, Marty must ensure his parents fall in love or risk erasing his own existence, all while finding a way back to the future. The film is a thrilling, humorous adventure that explores the ripple effects of our choices across time.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade', 'Indiana Jones seeks the Holy Grail.', 'Archaeologist Indiana Jones embarks on a quest to find the legendary Holy Grail, teaming up with his estranged father, Professor Henry Jones Sr. Their journey pits them against Nazis, ancient traps, and family secrets as they race to unlock the Grail’s mysteries. The film blends action, humor, and heart, showcasing the enduring bond between father and son.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse', 'A multiverse adventure with Spider-Man.', 'Teenager Miles Morales is bitten by a radioactive spider and discovers he has superpowers, just as a rift in the multiverse brings together Spider-heroes from alternate realities. With the help of his new friends, Miles must learn what it means to be Spider-Man and save his city from a threat that could destroy all universes. The film is a visually inventive, heartfelt celebration of heroism and identity.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Finding Nemo', 'A father searches for his lost son.', 'After his son Nemo is captured by divers, timid clownfish Marlin embarks on a daring journey across the ocean, joined by the forgetful but optimistic Dory. Facing sharks, jellyfish, and the vast unknown, Marlin learns to trust others and let go. Finding Nemo is an animated adventure filled with humor, heart, and breathtaking underwater worlds.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Social Network', 'The dramatic story of Facebook’s creation.', 'Chronicling the dramatic rise of Facebook, the film follows Harvard student Mark Zuckerberg as he creates a social networking site that revolutionizes communication. As Facebook’s popularity explodes, Mark faces legal battles and personal betrayals from friends and rivals. The Social Network is a gripping exploration of ambition, innovation, and the high cost of success in the digital age.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Silence of the Lambs', 'An FBI agent consults a brilliant killer.', 'FBI trainee Clarice Starling seeks the help of imprisoned cannibalistic killer Dr. Hannibal Lecter to catch another serial murderer, Buffalo Bill. As Clarice delves deeper into the case, she must navigate Lecter’s psychological games and confront her own fears. The film is a chilling, suspenseful thriller that delves into the darkest corners of the human mind.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Wolf of Wall Street', 'The rise and fall of a stockbroker.', 'Based on the true story of stockbroker Jordan Belfort, the film chronicles his meteoric rise and spectacular fall in the world of finance. Fueled by greed, drugs, and excess, Jordan’s relentless pursuit of wealth leads to wild parties, criminal schemes, and eventual downfall. The Wolf of Wall Street is a darkly comedic look at ambition, corruption, and the consequences of unchecked indulgence.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('Iron Man', 'A billionaire becomes an armored hero,', 'After being kidnapped by terrorists, billionaire inventor Tony Stark builds a high-tech armored suit to escape captivity. Returning home, he refines the suit and vows to use his technology for good, transforming himself into the superhero Iron Man. When a betrayal within his own company threatens global security, Stark must rely on his intelligence and new identity to save the day and redefine his legacy.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('The Revenant', 'A man struggles to survive in the wild.', 'Frontiersman Hugh Glass is left for dead after a brutal bear attack and betrayal by his own hunting team. Driven by sheer willpower and the desire for justice, Glass endures freezing wilderness, starvation, and relentless pursuit to survive. The Revenant is a raw, immersive tale of endurance, revenge, and the indomitable human spirit.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE),
('La La Land', 'A musical romance about love and dreams.', 'Aspiring actress Mia and jazz musician Sebastian meet and fall in love while pursuing their dreams in Los Angeles. As their careers take off, they must navigate the challenges of ambition, sacrifice, and the bittersweet realities of love. La La Land is a vibrant, heartfelt musical that celebrates the magic of dreams and the city of stars.', 0.0, FALSE, FALSE);